text: Colobothea fasciatipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Linsley in 1935. It is known from Honduras and Panama.BioLib.cz - Colobothea fasciatipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1935
title: Colobothea fasciatipennis
